	(text "Calorimetry rig MCU board — STM32F407VGT6 + AD5660 DAC + LTC2400 ADC\nBachmann 1972 relaxation method.  Pulse width = τ(6) ms = 4 ms baseline.\nADC at 16 ms cadence (62.5 Hz output rate after ΣΔ decimation)."
