	(text "4 interlocks (= τ(6)): StageTempLow + PulseRateExcess + HostTimeout + AdcDropout.\nBCS specific-heat anchor: ΔC/γTc = σ(6)/(7·ζ(3)) ≈ 1.4257 (verified).\nCernox sample mount on dilution-fridge stage (10 mK base, 0.3 K with ³He fridge alt)."
